org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_DesignModel.SRM.SW_Interaction

Interface NotificationResource

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Resource, SwInteractionResource, SwResource, SwSynchronizationResource, SynchronizationResource
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    NotificationResourceImpl

    public interface NotificationResource
extends SwSynchronizationResource
    A representation of the model object 'Notification Resource'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Occurence
    • Mechanism
    • Occurence Count Elements
    • Mask Elements
    • Flush Services
    • Signal Services
    • Wait Services
    • Clear Services
    See Also:
    SW_InteractionPackage.getNotificationResource()
